reference.Refstring: Al Balushi, T., Khod, O., Sampaio, P. R. F., Patel, M., Manchester, B. S. W., Corcho, O., & Loucopoulos, P. (2008). Identifying NFRs conflicts using quality ontologies. Combining SOA and BPM Technologies for Cross-System Process Automation, 929.

descriptions.definition: "NFRs [...] conflict with each other when they make contradicting statements about some software attribute, and they cooperate when they mutually enforce such attributes."
